text: It depends on what you have, but just focussing on the best stuff you have, material you’re proud of and can talk about, that’s the stuff to go with. If you only have one piece like that and it’s 10 seconds long, no matter, if you have 3 like that and it comes in at 30", no matter. Just make sure it’s as good as it can be.
Thanks, I'll bear that in mind
